Ummah College of Health Sciences and Technology (UCHSTG) bụ ụlọ akwụkwọ agụmakwụkwọ dị elu dị na Gombe State, Nigeria
E hiwere ya n'afọ 2016, wee malite ịrụ ọrụ n'afọ 2017
Ọ bụ otu n'ime kọleji nke sayensị ahụike na steeti Gombe, ndị ọzọ gụnyere College of Health Tech Kaltungo, na College of Health Sciences Medical na Tech, Gombe.
